{"tid":2295746,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃唔係大撚晒］","createTime":"2020-11-22T04:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T04:41:18.000Z","uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"748273fd526b482e2c4b4ff15ea47d13d2f91801","tid":2295746,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟之前上網搵工見到有間教育機構喺啲請手足嘅群入面請人，咁我就去見啦，interview嗰陣都好地地，但人工話只俾到$4x/hr遲啲有機會加...<br />\n<br />\nok,我當我冇教學經驗我照返，咁頭一兩個月都正正常常返工，第三個月只編幾日更俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果淨計返嗰間嘢成個月收入唔夠$2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（好彩當時有返其他part time先勉強夠嗰個月開支）<br />\n<br />\n咁我當咁啱間嘢因為疫情而冇乜學生，咁我就搵第二份part time，依家簽埋約，一個月平均返10～20日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但間教育機構就話想我返工，大概一個月10日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我就諗住依家返緊嗰份唔洗返嘅時候我可以去幫吓手，點知佢要求我要返足咁多日先可以俾我返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁啱我又有啲日子撞咗，所以冇返間教育機構<br />\n<br />\n其實我打咁大篇野係想講喺得請手足群請人都係想幫手足生活，但如果令到手足一個月唔夠2000，咁手足嗰個月點生活？如果你話可以炒兩份就話啫，但問題係你又要人返足先俾返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果要stand by等你份工，一早餓死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"> 咪撚壓榨手足  </span></span>"},{"pid":"6f41582785bf867bfd5ac2e9a1d121f2d778ad49","tid":2295746,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"2000不如唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5347481144e8e4654e39cd1812081519c52fbd1","tid":2295746,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f41582785bf867bfd5ac2e9a1d121f2d7